div.div:
The protagonist, Naoya, is a first-year in high school. He asks out Saki, a girl he has been in love with, and she agrees to be his girlfriend. He's currently on cloud nine. But then, a beautiful girl named Nagisa comes up to Naoya one day and tells him that she wants to go out with him. Naoya feels himself wavering because Nagisa is such a good girl, and he comes to a decision! A new kind of romcom from a rather unexpected decision is about to begin!
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Action, Drama, Horror, Mystery, Psychological, Supernatural

The suspense horror/dark fantasy story is set in Tokyo, which is haunted by mysterious "ghouls" who are devouring humans. People are gripped by the fear of these ghouls whose identities are masked in mystery. An ordinary college student named Kaneki encounters Rize, a girl who is an avid reader like him, at the café he frequents. Little does he realize that his fate will change overnight.
(Source: Anime News Network)
Pashirare Incha ga Jitsu wa Saikyou Datta Ken
Note: Includes a mini-manga drawn by Rokui Shirabe.

Love is always troubling. You want to have the courage to tell someone how you feel. You want to know who he likes. You want someone to listen to your worries. You want someone to give you a push. I know how you feel, and it hurts. Because I had a past I couldn't forget. And because now I have the "power" to save them.... That's why I, Io Akashi, became an angel. "I've finally found you, the angel of Kuze High." The angel touched the girl's cheek, in order to correct Yuzuki Minato's abnormal tendency to fall in love. This is a slightly mysterious coming-of-age story where memory and love play out softly.
(Source: Dengeki Bunko, translated)
